Cam::

She watched the baby bot suck down the energon in the bottle. She 
looked around hoping to find another one, but couldn't see it while 
standing there with the baby. She looked at the infant,"You know, if 
your a baby bot, that makes me a big bot now. So you know what? I'm 
going to have to take care of you untill your mommy and daddy get 
home. I just hope it's soon. Your bottle is almost empty."
